The '''''Crèche''''' was a [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[clustership]] under the command of [[Chine-kal]]. Following the [[Battle of Gyndine]], a number of prisoners of war (including [[Wurth Skidder]], [[Randa Besadii Diori]], and [[Roa]]) were taken aboard the ''Crèche'' to serve the developing [[yammosk]]s.

The vessel was destroyed during the [[Battle of Fondor]], when [[Kyp Durron]] and [[Ganner Rhysode]] boarded the ''Crèche'' to free the prisoners held aboard. Rhysode threw his [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber]] into the yammosk, and the vessel subsequently died.

